description: A standout layout with two private outdoor spaces: a landscaped rear patio for entertaining and a front-facing deck off the living room. Thoughtful design throughout with high ceilings, garage parking, and elevator access. Located in the heart of South Boston near the waterfront, parks, and restaurants.
